data.eml:eml: New species of the genus Gnathochorisis Förster (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae: Orthocentrinae) from the Neotropical Region

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Humala, Andrei E. (2017): New species of the genus Gnathochorisis Förster (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae: Orthocentrinae) from the Neotropical Region. Zootaxa 4250 (3): 201-218, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4250.3.1
